FT  07 OCT 93 / Research project could provide model for northern England
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
A RESEARCH project to show how state aid offered to manufacturing industry
in other European countries could provide a model for the north was launched
yesterday.
The analysis, at Newcastle University and the Newcastle-based Trades Union
Studies Information Unit, will examine the strengthening of four sectors of
the northern economy.
